title: Testing Resolution and etc.

embed.description: Here is LIMBO. An Indie game that seems really cool. How many deaths do I get in this EP? : Sorry for the random cut off, Since there is no "Chapter X ends" Its hard for me to know how much time has passed and even when the next part begins.

body:
Can someone tell me if the resolution and stuff is ok?
I think I have isolated what was causing stretching and other stupid annoying shit.

Watch for like 10-15 secs to see if everything is ok.
Thank you.
